sentences:
" I Am Woman " is a song performed by American recording artist Jordin Sparks .
The up - tempo song was written by Ali Pierre Gaschani , Dean Josiah and Ryan Tedder , who also produced the track .
" I Am Woman " premiered online via AOL Music on May 5 , 2011 , and was later officially released in the United States on May 10 , 2011 .
The song 's lyrics contain a message towards female empowerment , which talks about different aspects of the lives of women .
" I Am Woman " received a positive reception from most music critics , who complimented its differences with any of Sparks ' previous singles , as well as noting its similarities to the sounds of American R&B ; singer Beyoncé .
